            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;
                &lt;div class="comment"&gt;AAP-2.E part b&lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;!-- Question 6 --&gt;
                &lt;div class="assessment-data" type="multiplechoice" identifier="What's equivalent to num less than or equal to 23?"
