    &lt;p&gt;Many technologies are developed for military purposes and turn out also to be useful for the rest of us.&lt;/p&gt;

    &lt;div class="forYouToDo"&gt;
        &lt;ol start="2"&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Brainstorm as big a list as you can of &lt;strong&gt;dual-use technologies&lt;/strong&gt;.  (It doesn't count as dual-use if a technology developed for everyone to use, such as the telephone, is useful to the military in the same way that it's useful to anyone.)&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ol&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

    ## Should You Work on Military Technology? 
