&lt;body&gt;
    ## Guess My Numbersubtitle: "Unit , Lab , Page"
order:

    &lt;div class="learn"&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In this lab&lt;/strong&gt;, you will use two different algorithms to search a list, and you will learn that algorithms are categorized by the time required to run them.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;On this page&lt;/strong&gt;, you will modify your number guessing game from Unit 2 to make the computer do the guessing.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="forYouToDo" id="first"&gt;
        &lt;ol&gt;
