            &lt;li&gt; 
                Click the picture to load a version of the number guessing game in which you guess a number from 1 to 60. &lt;br /&gt;
                &lt;a class="run" href="/prog/5-algorithms/U5L1-GuessNumber.xml"&gt; &lt;img class="indent" src="/img/5-algorithms/number-guessing-game.png" alt="number guessing game" title="number guessing game"/&gt; &lt;/a&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
