    ## Transposing Music
    &lt;div class="forYouToDo"&gt;
        &lt;ol start="9"&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;
                &lt;img class="imageRight" src="/img/icons/talk-with-your-partner-mini.png" alt="Talk with Your Partner" title="Talk with Your Partner" /&gt;
                Compare the output of these two scripts that you created above. Discuss what &lt;code&gt;map + 5&lt;/code&gt; does to the sounds you hear:&lt;br /&gt;
                &lt;img class="indent" src="/img/3-lists/compare-play-note-2.png" alt="for each (note) of (list (60) (64) (67) (72) (60)) (play note (note) for (1) beats)" title="for each (note) of (list (60) (64) (67) (72) (60)) (play note (note) for (1) beats)"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
