                    &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Try playing your song using your &lt;code&gt;transpose&lt;/code&gt; block with several different shift numbers so that you can &lt;em&gt;hear&lt;/em&gt; the impact of &lt;code&gt;map&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
