    &lt;p&gt;

    &lt;/p&gt;

    ## Finding Your Communities in Tech
    &lt;div class="forYouToDo"&gt;
        &lt;ol&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;
                Learn bit a about a few communities that interest you.
                &lt;ul&gt;
                    &lt;img class="imageRight" src="/img/icons/talk-with-your-partner.png" alt="Talk with Your Partner" title="Talk with Your Partner" /&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;How is the organization structured?&lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;How big is the organization?&lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;What kind of support do they offer?&lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;Do they host events? If so, where?&lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;Do they use social media platforms?&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;/ul&gt;

                &lt;div class="endnote"&gt;
                    Some examples of communitites for groups underrepresented in computer science are listed below. There are many, many more groups out there!
                    &lt;ul&gt;
                        &lt;ul&gt;
                            &lt;li&gt;
                                Black Communities
                                &lt;ul&gt;
                                    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://blacktechnation.com/" title="Black Tech Nation" target="_blank"&gt;Black Tech Nation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
                                    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://devcolor.org/" title="/dev/color" target="_blank"&gt;/dev/color&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
                                    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.blacksintechnology.net/" title="Blacks In Technology" target="_blank"&gt;Blacks In Technology&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
                                    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="" title="" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
                                &lt;/ul&gt;
                            &lt;/li&gt;
                            &lt;li&gt;
                                Youth Communities
                                &lt;ul&gt;
                                    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.blackgirlscode.com/" title="Black Girls Code" target="_blank"&gt;Black Girls Code&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
